divs: Sighting DetailsStanding outside in the evening, something drew attention. Not easily seen but once spotted knew it was UFO. Its shape was like an egg when dropped in a pan, not exactly sphere shaped. Huge, as large as a city block. Jet plane flew in front of and seemed like a spec in comparison. 40 jets could have fit the size of this craft. UFO hovered, witnessed for 5 minutes. Had a feeling like "there is something going on here. I don't know what, but sense is a big deal".
